<bibRefCitation id="EFC7269D5549B03305C257E9FCFCF7E4" author="Gunther" box="[739,882,977,999]" pageId="5" pageNumber="216" refId="ref4047" refString="M e a s u r e m e n t s (after Gunther, 1939 and Shishodia, 1991). Length: body: ♀ 11.0; pronotum: ♀ 10.0; hind femur: ♀ 5.5; ovipositor 1.3." type="journal volume" year="1939">Günther, 1939</bibRefCitation>
, с изменениями; 20 по: Shishodia, 1991).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE95B6C5549B03307C250E5FB2BF13B" blockId="5.[174,1233,1085,1528]" pageId="5" pageNumber="216">Coloured as male, but second segment of fore and mid tarsi, as well as third segment of hind tarsus with broad light brown ring near middle. Hind tibia brown with light ring in basal third. Subgenital plate, epiproct and ovipositor blackish brown.</paragraph>
